Package: aodv2
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         python3 (>= 3.11),
         python3-venv (>= 3.11),
         systemd
Description: Always-on diagnostics daemon for Linux NFS and SMB filesystems
 Always-on Diagnostics daemon for monitoring Linux NFS and SMB anomalies and
 automatic log-collection.
 .
 The daemon is installed under /opt/aodv2 and runs from a self-contained
 Python virtual environment built at install time. Configuration lives in
 /etc/aodv2/config.yaml; the output directory is user-tunable via the
 aod_output_dir key in that file and is created by the daemon on first use.
